          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Fair Pay for All Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits sex discrimination in the payment of the minimum wage to workers based on their gender identity, sexual orientation, sex characteristics, a sex stereotype, pregnancy, childbirth, or a related medical condition.</p>]]></text>
